Package lubiku.castleQuest.Configuration

Class JSONConfigWriter

java.lang.Object
lubiku.castleQuest.Configuration.JSONConfigWriter
public class JSONConfigWriter extends Object

JSONConfigWriter

The JSONConfigWriter class is responsible for creating a JSON configuration file for a game. It takes input from the MainController and GamePanel classes to collect the necessary data. It then converts this data into a JSON string and writes it to a temporary save file using the Gson library.
